snippet.title: Bombslinger Release Date Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Bombslinger is a Wild West action-maze game filled with explosive single player action and hectic 4 player deathmatch battles! Coming April 11 2018 on Nintendo Switch, Microsoft XBOX One, Steam.

Bombslinger is currently in development on Steam Early Access
http://store.steampowered.com/app/475960
